1942;;Take a Letter, Darling;;American;;Mitchell Leisen;;Rosalind Russell, Fred MacMurray;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Take_a_Letter,_Darling;;A struggling painter (Fred MacMurray) takes a job as private secretary to a tough female advertising executive (Rosalind Russell). While working together to win the account of a tobacco company, they end up falling in love.[3]